Wallace Reid https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wallace_Reid 0 William Wallace Halleck Reid (April 15, 1891 – January 18, 1923) was an American actor in silent film referred to as "the screen's most perfect lover". Reid also had a brief career as a racing driver.
